28
00:01:37,060 --> 00:01:38,120
[Nanwu University]

29
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,070
Is that Sang Yan?

30
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,000
Hurry up.

31
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:40,950
Let's go check it out.

32
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,310
He's so handsome.

33
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,640
He's so fair.

34
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:45,430
Exactly.

35
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,840
He's so tall. I want his WeChat.

36
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,000
Let's go check it out.

37
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,640
Sang Yan!

38
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,230
He heard us!

39
00:01:51,230 --> 00:01:52,150
Didn't he hear us?

40
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,430
Quiet down. He can hear everything.

41
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:55,790
What's going on?

42
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,000
They said I'm good-looking,

43
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,000
and they want to add me on WeChat.

44
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,640
Isn't that pretty common?

45
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,480
Well, to you, I guess it's true.

46
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,870
The National Day holiday is approaching.

47
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,680
What's your plan?

48
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,470
I have no plan.

49
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,280
How about you?

50
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,280
I'm going back to Yihe.

51
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,150
Why don't you come with me?

52
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,470
You seem interested in my hometown.

53
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,280
Let's talk later.

54
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,150
"Let's talk later..."

55
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,630
You sound like I'm begging you.

56
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:22,750
If you don't want to, forget it.

57
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,840
Are we still eating or not?

58
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:34,220
[Yihe University]

59
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:43,030
Jiang.

60
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,470
Jiang.

61
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:52,360
I've been waiting here for half a day.

62
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,870
Did you see me for something?

63
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,990
Can't I just come to check on you?

64
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,590
By the way, I brought you some chili sauce.

65
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,750
It's the kind you loved when you were a kid.

66
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,360
I also brought you some local specialties.

67
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,310
I've quit eating spicy food for a long time.

68
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:09,240
That's okay.

69
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:10,680
You can give it to your dorm mates.

70
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,800
They'll definitely like it.

71
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,590
Here you go.

72
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,270
Thank you.

73
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,150
No need to be polite.

74
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:25,470
I'm leaving now.

75
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,360
Wait...

76
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:30,800
Mom!

77
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:32,640
Take it quickly.

78
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,710
Take it.

79
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,590
We're still going to the pedestrian street.

80
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:36,550
Hurry up.

81
00:03:36,550 --> 00:03:38,470
Okay, I'll be done in a second.

82
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,150
Why didn't you greet your sister?

83
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,680
Hello.

84
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,310
What's good to eat or do in Yihe?

85
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:47,310
Can you recommend something?

86
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,470
I'm not very familiar.

87
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,470
You're attending Yihe University. How can you not be familiar?

88
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,710
Alright, let's finish up.

89
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,960
Go rest now.

90
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,470
Let's go, Mom.

91
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:14,180
[Episode 17]
[The Farthest Distance]

92
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,020
[3355 days]

93
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,320
Smile!

94
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,590
Look at her little hands!

95
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,560
Good girl.

96
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:31,520
Who is it?

97
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,640
[Day 293 of Living Together]

98
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,470
They're so small.

99
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,670
Look at her little hands.

100
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:37,790
Su Tian,

101
00:04:37,790 --> 00:04:38,790
may I hug?

102
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:40,320
How can you hug her?

103
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,270
Only I can.

104
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:45,470
I didn't mean to hug Su Tian.

105
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,000
I meant I want to hug the baby.

106
00:04:47,030 --> 00:04:47,670
That's not okay either.

107
00:04:47,910 --> 00:04:48,790
Let me hug her...

108
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,960
Did you wash your hands?

109
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,960
You have to wash your hands first.

110
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:51,520
I washed them.

111
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,880
I even sanitized them with alcohol.

112
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,320
Take her out.

113
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,150
Let me take you out.

114
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:55,880
Take care.

115
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,790
Do it gently.

116
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:01,590
Take your time.

117
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,000
Right.

118
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:09,760
Let me hug her.

119
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:14,670
There are still

120
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,640
56 days left.

121
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,520
How come you're out?

122
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,030
Just checking on you.

123
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:26,030
How's it going?

124
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:26,710
Tell me quickly.

125
00:05:28,110 --> 00:05:28,910
Well,

126
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:30,960
I'm still working on it.

127
00:05:31,110 --> 00:05:32,470
No progress at all?

128
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,230
Is he keeping you hanging?

129
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,000
No.

130
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,840
He probably doesn't know I'm pursuing him.

131
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:39,320
So, your relationship

132
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,790
hasn't progressed at all?

133
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,080
I'm not really sure.

134
00:05:43,470 --> 00:05:45,110
Didn't you do anything at all?

135
00:05:46,470 --> 00:05:47,590
Not exactly.

136
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:49,790
It's just

137
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,710
that I don't know where to start.

138
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:54,000
You could start with his hobbies.

139
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,200
Hobbies?

140
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,080
Do you know how to play?

141
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,960
Use your skills!

142
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,110
What does a basic attack mean?

143
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,590
Can you focus on your fire?

144
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,350
What's up?

145
00:06:12,350 --> 00:06:13,400
Did the other side pay you to play like this?

146
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,270
Why are you playing like that?

147
00:06:20,590 --> 00:06:21,200
What's wrong?

148
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,440
Nothing.

149
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:30,840
You seem like a different person

150
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,670
when you're playing games.

151
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:38,520
Keep playing.

152
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:39,880
I'll take a break.

153
00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:49,180
E-sports sometimes involve

154
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,320
some verbal sparring.

155
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:50,840
It's...

156
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:52,760
it's totally normal.

157
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,640
What a kid!

158
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,790
He'd skip meals

159
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,880
just to play games.

160
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:03,760
He's been playing this game a lot recently.

161
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,520
How's it?

162
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,150
It's pretty fun.

163
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,080
I used to play it in college.

164
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:10,590
But I haven't played in a long time.

165
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:12,840
It feels a bit rusty now.

166
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,440
You're playing it yourself?

167
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,150
You can play with him!

168
00:07:18,150 --> 00:07:20,200
What's the point of playing by yourself?

169
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,790
I'm too bad at it.

170
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:23,400
I'm afraid he'll criticize me.

171
00:07:23,790 --> 00:07:24,910
No way.

172
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:27,080
When you play games with boys,

173
00:07:27,150 --> 00:07:29,520
they just feel superior like they're helping a girl out.

174
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:30,400
So,

175
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:32,080
no matter how bad you play,

176
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,520
they won't criticize you.

177
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:34,640
No.

178
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,520
He won't treat me any differently just because it's me.

179
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,150
Hello.

180
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:39,670
Hello.

181
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:41,670
Yifan,

182
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,150
you play this game too?

183
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,270
This game is slow to level up

184
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:47,230
if no one's helping.

185
00:07:47,230 --> 00:07:48,150
Want me to help you level up?

186
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:49,520
No need. I'm not in a hurry.

187
00:07:50,670 --> 00:07:52,110
Mobile games

188
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,640
are boring to play alone.

189
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:58,940
[Add friend: Mr. Mu.]

190
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,640
[Friend added successfully]
Done.

191
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,790
I'm online all night

192
00:08:01,790 --> 00:08:03,470
if you need help, Yifan,

193
00:08:03,470 --> 00:08:04,440
just call me anytime.

194
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,200
Have you had lunch?

195
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,230
Yeah. I just finished.

196
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:16,030
Have you sorted the files?

197
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:21,510
Looks like...

198
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:22,920
not yet.

199
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:31,960
Okay.

200
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,400
Thank you.

201
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,320
Thanks for your hard work.

202
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,680
Sang Yan.

203
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,350
Where are you going?

204
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:45,590
Where else would I go?

205
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,800
Going home after work.

206
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:47,630
Going home?

207
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,750
Did you forget that you promised

208
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:50,750
to join me at Overtime tonight?

209
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:53,870
Do we have to do it today?

210
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:54,560
Of course, it has to be today.

211
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,590
Today's the shareholders' meeting.

212
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,680
I've already made plans with Qian Fei and Chen Junwen.

213
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,280
They're just waiting for us. Let's go.

214
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,160
Come on,

215
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:02,870
let's go!

216
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,960
The drinks and dishes are here!

217
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,710
The dishes, drinks, and Sang Yan are here!

218
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:10,840
You're here.

219
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:13,840
What a rare guest,

220
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,320
Mr. Sang.

221
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:17,920
Mr. Qian has been giving me a hard time recently.

222
00:09:18,110 --> 00:09:20,280
It's definitely not that serious.

223
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:22,840
It's just that recently, the shareholders

224
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,750
can't get a grasp on your movements.

225
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,040
Tell us about it.

226
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:27,280
Seriously?

227
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:27,870
Seriously, tell us.

228
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,630
If I really tell you, I'm afraid you'll feel off.

229
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,630
You might get so jealous that you'd lose your cool.

230
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,630
You could even get really mad.

231
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,350
Hey,

232
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:34,800
what does he mean by that?

233
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,710
He said

234
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,350
there's a girl chasing him recently.

235
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:38,630
He doesn't have time for us.

236
00:09:38,990 --> 00:09:39,870
What's the big deal?

237
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:40,960
Are you crazy?

238
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,800
It's not like this is the first time someone's chasing you.

239
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:44,840
We've never seen him show off like this before.

240
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,560
Right?

241
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,320
You like her too, don't you?

242
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:50,110
Yes.

243
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,960
So what?

244
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,040
Really?

245
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:53,920
Who?

246
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,870
Let me figure this out.

247
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,630
You like her too,

248
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,110
but you're waiting for her to come chase you?

249
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,230
That's kind of passive.

250
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,510
You're a man.

251
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:03,960
You can't just keep her hanging.

252
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,040
Qian Fei,

253
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:08,390
do I need you to teach me?

254
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:11,230
If you had even a fraction of my emotional intelligence,

255
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,750
you wouldn't be playing backup in college.

256
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,630
Stop!

257
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:15,800
I'll take the punishment.

258
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:17,870
Honestly, Sang Yan.

259
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:20,840
You always rub salt in others' wounds.

260
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,040
And this is from ages ago.

261
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,160
Every time there's a gathering,

262
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,200
you bring it up.

263
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:28,040
Is it that new intern from our company?

264
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,040
She's probably a junior or senior.

265
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:30,160
She's quite pretty.

266
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,320
Wow, you,

267
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,560
an old dog chasing a young pup.

268
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,990
She's still in college.

269
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:35,470
I got it.

270
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,040
He likes younger girls.

271
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,040
Get lost.

272
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:39,350
Love

273
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,590
has nothing to do with age.

274
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:42,560
Right, Jun?

275
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,350
You two together,

276
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:45,960
even if she's five to ten years younger,

277
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,920
it doesn't matter.

278
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,200
Looks like it's not that intern.

279
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,560
Is it

280
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,470
the girl who joined the company with you?

281
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:53,800
Wrong again?

282
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,840
What are your plans with that girl?

283
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:57,840
What plans?

284
00:10:58,590 --> 00:10:59,680
She wants to chase me.

285
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,470
What can I do?

286
00:11:01,230 --> 00:11:02,230
Just wait to be chased.

