407
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:22,840
If you locked the door, I definitely wouldn't have gotten in.

408
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,110
You'd pick the lock.

409
00:20:24,430 --> 00:20:25,720
I don't have that skill.

410
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:26,950
You do.

411
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:29,800
For the sake of invading me,

412
00:20:29,910 --> 00:20:31,150
