454
00:23:19,560 --> 00:23:20,630
I came to check on him.

455
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:22,110
Let's eat together.

456
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,840
Is this the visit you were talking about yesterday?

457
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:31,630
